data.title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2015 Ford Mustang GT 5.0L
data.tags: K&N Cold Air Intake, 2015 Ford Mustang GT, how to install K&N air intake, Mustang GT 5.0, k and n, k&n, cold air intake
data.description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N air intake on your 2015 Ford Mustang GT 5.0L.

K&N 63-2590 performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2015 Ford Mustang GT with a 5.0L engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 17.41 horsepower at 5287 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 63-2590 also includes a rotomolded polyethylene intake tube with an aluminum heat shield to increase air flow while isolating intake air from engine heat.

data.title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2005-2014 Toyota Tacoma 4.0L
data.tags: K&N Air Intake, Cold air intake, CAI, how to install, Toyota Tacoma, how to install k&n intake
data.description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N Air Intake on your 2005 to 2014 Toyota Tacoma 4.0L.

K&N 57-9025 performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2005 to 2014 Toyota Tacoma with a 4.0L engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 8.91 horsepower at 4857 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 57-9025 also includes a custom rotomolded intake tube and aluminum heat shield to isolate intake air from engine heat.  It also maintains use of the factory hydrocarbon trap.

data.tags: K&N Cold Air Intake, CAI, Subaru WRX, how to install, k&n air intake, cold air intake, subaru performance parts, wrx
data.description:
